The National Working Committee of the Peoples Democratic Party has announced that it will present a certificate of return to the party’s presidential flag bearer Abubakar Atiku. Atiku won the party’s presidential ticket during a special national convention held in Abuja on May 28 through 29, 2022 after scoring 371 votes. The national publicity secretary of the party, Debo Ologunagba, in a statement said all governors, governorship candidates, presidential aspirants, members of the Board of Trustees, members of the National Assembly, other candidates of the party and all critical stakeholders are expected to grace the special ceremony. The statement further said the event would hold on Wednesday, June 1, 2022, by noon at the PDP National Secretariat, Abuja. Copyright PUNCH. All rights reserved. This material, and other digital content on this website, may not be reproduced, published, broadcast, rewritten or redistributed in whole or in part without prior express written permission from PUNCH. Contact: theeditor@punchng.com